{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/teaser-gundala-abimana-aryasatya/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Teaser Gundala Terungkap Bersama Pemeran Filmnya!","content":"<p>Setelah hening beberapa waktu lamanya, akhirnya detil tentang adaptasi film Gundala mulai terungkap. Untuk pertama kalinya, teaser Gundala serta visual perdananya diungkap pertama kali di acara Indonesia Comic Con 2018.</p>\n<p>Sebelumnya di bulan April 2018 lalu, BumiLangit bersama Screenplay Films dan Legacy Pictures mengumumkan bahwa mereka akan memproduksi film Gundala, sosok <em>superhero</em> Indonesia ciptaan legenda komik Hasmi. Tak tanggung-tanggung, sutradara visioner Joko Anwar sendiri yang menukangi proyek film ini.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga:Â <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/joko-anwar-sutradara-film-gundala/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Joko Anwar Akan Menyutradarai Film Gundala!</a></strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51468\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51468\" data-attachment-id=\"51468\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/teaser-gundala-abimana-aryasatya/attachment/01-teaser-gundala/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01-teaser-gundala.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-teaser-gundala\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01-teaser-gundala-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01-teaser-gundala.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51468\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01-teaser-gundala.jpg\" alt=\"First look kostum Gundala. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01-teaser-gundala.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/01-teaser-gundala-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51468\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">First look kostum Gundala. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div>\n<p>Pada tanggal 28 Oktober lalu di Jakarta Convention Center, <em>teaser</em> Gundala untuk pertama kalinya ditayangkan ke hadapan publik. <em>Teaser</em> sepanjang hampir 30 detik ini tidak mengungkap hal krusial seperti plot, kecuali beberapa tokoh sentral dan suasana filmnya.</p>\n<p>Bersamaan dengan itu pula, para pemain film Gundala diperkenalkan. Abimana Aryasatya terpilih memerankan Sancaka, seorang petugas keamanan yang kelak akan berubah menjadi <em>superhero</em> Gundala. Artis cilik Muzaki terpilih memerankan Sancaka muda.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51469\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51469\" data-attachment-id=\"51469\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/teaser-gundala-abimana-aryasatya/attachment/02-teaser-gundala/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/02-teaser-gundala.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-teaser-gundala\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/02-teaser-gundala-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/02-teaser-gundala.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51469\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/02-teaser-gundala.jpg\" alt=\"Abimana Aryasatya, Muzaki, Tara Basro, dan Bront Palarae. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/02-teaser-gundala.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/02-teaser-gundala-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51469\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Abimana Aryasatya, Muzaki, Tara Basro, dan Bront Palarae. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div>\n<p>Kemudian, dua lakon utama Pengabdi Setan, Tara Basro dan Bront Palarae memerankan dua karakter sentral; Tara sebagai jurnalis Wulan (identitas asli <em>superhero</em> Merpati, juga ciptaan Hasmi), dan Bront sebagai musuh utama Gundala: Pengkor. Lewat <em>teaser</em> Gundala juga dipastikan Rio Dewanto terlibat dalam film ini sebagai sosok yang diduga kuat merupakan ayah Sancaka. Sebelumnya di bulan Juni, bintang film The Raid 2 Cecep Arif Rahman akan berkontribusi <a href=\"https://hot.detik.com/movie/d-4063449/cecep-arif-rahman-tengah-terlibat-di-produksi-film-gundala\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">sebagai koreografer aksi</a> film ini.</p>\n<h2>Gundala Sosok Superhero Manusiawi</h2>\n<div id=\"attachment_51470\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51470\" data-attachment-id=\"51470\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/teaser-gundala-abimana-aryasatya/attachment/03-teaser-gundala/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/03-teaser-gundala.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-teaser-gundala\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/03-teaser-gundala-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/03-teaser-gundala.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51470\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/03-teaser-gundala.jpg\" alt=\"Teaser Gundala tampilkan origin story Sancaka. Sumber: BumiLangit\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/03-teaser-gundala.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/03-teaser-gundala-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51470\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Teaser Gundala tampilkan <em>origin story</em> Sancaka. Sumber: BumiLangit</p></div>\n<p>Joko Anwar mengaku sudah membidik Abimana untuk memerankan Gundala sejak lama. Bagi Joko, Abimana memiliki kualitas yang tepat untuk memerankan sosok Sancaka yang tangguh namun juga rapuh. Meski demikian, awalnya Abimana enggan untuk terlibat dalam produksi film Gundala. &#8220;Sempat diminta (produser) cari aktor pengganti, gue bilang enggak, gue tunggu Abimana. Gue dekati Abimana, bukan cuma ngomong sendiri, tapi lewat banyak orang, temannya dan istrinya,&#8221; ungkap Joko menjelaskan proses perekrutan Abimana.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_51471\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51471\" data-attachment-id=\"51471\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/teaser-gundala-abimana-aryasatya/attachment/04-teaser-gundala/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04-teaser-gundala.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-teaser-gundala\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04-teaser-gundala-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04-teaser-gundala.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51471\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04-teaser-gundala.jpg\" alt=\"Abimana akan tampilkan dualitas sosok superhero Gundala. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04-teaser-gundala.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04-teaser-gundala-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51471\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Abimana akan tampilkan dualitas sosok superhero Gundala. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div>\n<p>Setelah didekati dengan berbagai cara, akhirnya Abimana pun menyepakati tawaran Joko. &#8220;Enggak tahu kebetulan apa enggak, hari terakhir saya seleksi kerja, Joko kirim draf skenario untuk dibaca. Saya balas &#8216;Enggak usah baca gue ikut, tapi satu hal kita harus saling percaya,'&#8221; tuturnya menyambung cerita Joko.</p>\n<p>Terkait alasan Joko memilihnya untuk memerankan Sancaka/Gundala, Abimana menjelaskan bahwa sosok karakter yang ia perankan merupakan seorang <em>superhero</em> yang sangat manusiawi. &#8220;Gundala punya rasa sakit dan bukan jagoan yang tidak terkalahkan. Ia bisa menangis, sakit, jatuh cinta, sakit hati, bingung, itu semua ada. Bukan jagoan yang kalau bosen pergi ke Bulan,&#8221; jelas Abimana.</p>\n<h2><em>Teaser</em> Gundala Sajikan Kisah <em>Superhero</em> <em>Grounded</em></h2>\n<div id=\"attachment_51472\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51472\" data-attachment-id=\"51472\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/teaser-gundala-abimana-aryasatya/attachment/05-teaser-gundala/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/05-teaser-gundala.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-teaser-gundala\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/05-teaser-gundala-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/05-teaser-gundala.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51472\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/05-teaser-gundala.jpg\" alt=\"Joko Anwar mengaku sebagai fans berat Gundala. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/05-teaser-gundala.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/05-teaser-gundala-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51472\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Joko Anwar mengaku sebagai fans berat Gundala. Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div>\n<p>Tantangan yang dirasakan oleh Joko Anwar saat menulis cerita Gundala adalah bagaimana caranya mengangkat kisah <em>superhero</em> era akhir 60-an itu menjadi lebih modern tanpa meninggalkan ciri khasnya. &#8220;Sensibilitasnya harus cocok dengan <em>society</em> zaman sekarang. Karena kalau kita plek ketiplek dari zaman dulu enggak bisa, harus di-<em>upgrade</em>,&#8221; terang Joko.</p>\n<p>Menurut Joko yang juga adalah fans Gundala, proses <em>upgrade</em> inilah yang ia lakukan pada film Pengabdi Setan agar penonton merasa <em>relate</em> dengan ceritanya. Untuk mencapai hal tersebut, Joko mengaku cukup kesulitan untuk mendapaytkan <em>mood</em> menulis yang bagus. &#8220;Sangat susah sampai nulis harus dalam kondisi sangat tenang. Kalau enggak di museum saya nulis di kuburan. Setelah empat bulan akhirnya jadi skenario Gundala,&#8221; candanya.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_45700\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45700\" data-attachment-id=\"45700\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/joko-anwar-sutradara-film-gundala/attachment/05-film-gundala/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-film-gundala.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-film-gundala\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-film-gundala-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-film-gundala.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45700\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-film-gundala.jpg\" alt=\"Gundala versi 1981. Sumber: Liputan6\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-film-gundala.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-film-gundala-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45700\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gundala versi 1981. Sumber: Liputan6</p></div>\n<p>Alasan Joko tersebut kurang lebih masuk akal, karena bisa jadi ia ingin membuat sosok Gundala versinya sendiri yang berbeda dengan Gundala yang pernah ada. Apalagi sebelumnya sudah pernah dibuat film Gundala tahun 1981. Film yang disutradarai Lilik Sudjio ini menampilkan Teddy Purba sebagai Sancaka/Gundala. Jika Gundala versi 1981 menyajikan <em>experience</em> yang dekat dengan komik, bisa diperkirakan Gundala versi Joko Anwar akan menawarkan pengalaman yang lebih realistis, <em>grounded</em>, serta <em>edgy</em>.</p>\n<p>Film Gundala tengah menjalani proses <em>shooting</em> hari ke-48 dari 55 hari yang direncanakan, dan dijadwalkan bakal segera tayang pada pertengahan tahun 2019. Penasaran seperti apa <em>teaser</em> Gundala? Kamu bisa menontonnya di bawah ini.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-8gKzImiN1c\" width=\"806\" height=\"336\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/genre/action\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-attachment-id=\"50177\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/karakter-metal-gear-solid-berkesan/attachment/print-8/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Action.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1534763889&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Print&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Banner Komik Action CIAYO Comics\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Action-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Action.jpg\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-50177\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Action.jpg\" alt=\"Banner Komik Action\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Action.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Komik-Action-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /></a></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"30447079-c984-5471-9284-22ecc2689bd2"}}}